 * DESCRIBEFIELD FEXDATE    AS EXDATE     USING GZFT101HPD                           :
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FDBTVDT    AS DBTVDT     USING GZFT101HPD                           :
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FINDATE    AS INDATE     USING GZFT101HPD                           :
 * DESCRIBEFIELD FUPDDTE    AS UPDDTE     USING GZFT101HPD                           :
 * DESCRIBEFIELD SHANDCG    AS HANDCG     USING GZFT101HPD                           :
***DESCRIBEFIELD BSHANDCG   AS HANDCG     USING GZFT101HPD (BASECCY)*****************:/*BUG5605*/
 * DESCRIBEFIELD CUSTZONE   AS A8ZONE     USING GZSDBRCHPD                           :
 * DESCRIBEEND                                                                       :
                                                                                     :
